{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::18121026674::vessel::669d65f0-da9c-11f0-90ba-894d3ae49d9a","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sardinia\n\nANTARES 32 FLY. boat rental in Cannigione Antares 32 has all the maritime qualities that contribute to the reputation of the Antares line and is designed to offer comfort to all passengers. This vessel is designed for those who want to admire the sea from above. In fact, from the large flybridge with a spacious L-shaped sofa, located behind the helm station, the sea becomes the only horizon. The comfortable cockpit, equipped with a sofa and table with chairs, is the ideal space to relax in company, while the bow sunbathing area offers a privileged spot for those who love to feel the sea. The Antares 32 has 2 spacious cabins, one with a double bed and the guest cabin with bunk beds, as well as a large bathroom. A bright sliding glass door gives us access to the interior, where the innovative layout makes the Antares 32 both comfortable and dynamic. At the entrance, we find a generous dinette, furnished with a comfortable sofa, and the internal helm area. In front of the sofa, we have a practical, bright kitchen, equipped with all the comforts Descending a few steps, we reach the sleeping area, where we find the two spacious cabins and the bathroom with electric toilet and shower. The entire space is enveloped in a cozy atmosphere thanks to the classic style and wooden finishes, making this rental boat in Sardinia perfect for your needs.","blueprint":{"name":"ANTARES 32 FLY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::669d65f0-da9c-11f0-90ba-894d3ae49d9a::assets::3240f090-da9e-11f0-bb7a-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::669d65f0-da9c-11f0-90ba-894d3ae49d9a::assets::32400630-da9e-11f0-bb79-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::669d65f0-da9c-11f0-90ba-894d3ae49d9a::assets::32400630-da9e-11f0-bb7a-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::669d65f0-d